    <p>In this screencast, we would learn how to use the <a href="https://drupal.org/project/google_chart_tools">google chart tools</a> in drupal for creating a simple analytics dashboard for our website. The <a href="https://developers.google.com/chart/?csw=1">google chart tools</a> allows us to create simple, custom and rich interactive live data for our website. For this screencast, we enabled the statistics module in drupal core to record view counts per node on the website. And then we created a simple dashboard showing interactive graphs of how often nodes were visited. We created samples using pie chart, line chart and column charts for our site. To achieve this, we used the views module in combination with the google chart tools.Â </p>
